OL,3,CFestive disappointment for West Brom
OL,4,Cfans as manager Carlos Corberan leaves
OL,6,FBy Tejinder Kaur-Thanki, ITV News
OL,7,FCentral Content Editor
OL,9,FWest Bromwich Albion have announced
OL,10,Ftheir manager Carlos Corberan is
OL,11,Fleaving the club after a two-year
OL,12,Fstint, to return to his homeland in
OL,13,FSpain.
OL,15,FThe 41-year old, who took over at the
OL,16,FHawthorns in October 2022, will now
OL,17,Ftake over La Liga side Valencia.
OL,19,FThe news is a big blow to fans with
OL,20,Fthe announcement coming early on
OL,21,FChristmas Day.
