OL,6,FIn a statement the club said:
OL,8,F"Albion have reached an agreement in
OL,9,Fprinciple for Carlos Corberan to
OL,10,Fdepart the club to pursue a new
OL,11,Fopportunity with La Liga side Valencia.
OL,13,F"The 41-year-old is set to return to
OL,14,Fhis homeland with the club's gratitude
OL,15,Fand best wishes following a two-year
OL,16,Ftenure at The Hawthorns.
OL,18,F"Chris Brunt, Damia Abella and Boaz
OL,19,FMyhill will oversee first-team duties
OL,20,Funtil further notice.
