OL,6,FMeanwhile the afore-mentioned club's
OL,7,FCEO & Sporting Director Andrew Nestor,
OL,8,Falso posted his thanks on social media
OL,9,Fto the exiting manager, writing:
OL,11,F"Thank you Carlos for your
OL,12,Fcontribution to this great club.
OL,14,F"The process to identify and appoint a
OL,15,Fsuccessor is already underway and we
OL,16,Fhave every faith in the team, led by
OL,17,FChris Brunt and Damia Abella, to
OL,18,Fcontinue our work on the pitch during
OL,19,Fthis interim period".
