OL,6,FCorberan represented Villareal as a
OL,7,Fyouth but retired to pursue a career
OL,8,Fin coaching.
OL,10,FHe had spells at Leeds United,
OL,11,FHuddersfield Town - where he took them
OL,12,Fto the Championship play-off final -
OL,13,Fand at Olympiacos.
OL,15,FHe also won EFL Championship Manager
OL,16,Fof the Month award in February 2022.
OL,18,F"It's breaking Baggies hearts that
OL,19,Fhe's leaving"
