OL,6,FOur Sports Correspondent Dan Salisbury-
OL,7,FJones spoke to some Baggies fans
OL,8,Foutside the Hawthorns before today's
OL,9,Fofficial announcement.
OL,11,FOne young fan told him it's
OL,12,Fheartbreaking to have this news so
OL,13,Fclose to Christmas:
OL,15,FCorberan leaves the club in seventh
OL,16,Fposition in the Championship table.
OL,18,FWest Brom next face Derby County at
OL,19,Fhome on Boxing Day.
